<p>
<seg id=1> The western tourists just freed in Yemen said that the kidnappers actually used them as a shield when Yemen government troops opened fire on the kidnappers in an attempt to save them. </seg>
<seg id=2> Four tourists were killed in the gunfire on Tuesday.  Twelve overcame the difficulty and were rescued. </seg>
<seg id=3> According to Yemen government, Yemen troops attacked the kidnappers because the circumstance indicated that some hostages were going to be killed. </seg>
<seg id=4> However, rescued tourists said that gunfire commenced only after Yemen troops started their rescue operation. </seg>
</p>
